    "For instance, consider the combination with either example-based or counterfactual, generative XAI.",
    "Under what conditions would it be better to combine saliency maps with (a) XAI methods that select example images from the dataset that the AI considers to be similar to the highlighted area (Fel et al., 2023) or (b) XAI methods that generate visualisations of the object perceived by the AI in the highlighted area (Giulivi et al., 2021)?",
